  "descriptionText": "Shipman 59 for sale 2014 Shipman 59 for sale is in very good condition and available for immediate viewings in Valencia, Spain. The carbon yacht Shipman 59 is the ultimate performance blue water cruiser thanks to her short-handed sailing and forward deck lounge area, her integrated Bimini and spray dodger, her protected steering station, the 360º view pilothouse and her carbon-epoxy construction. ''The Shipman 59 for sale 2014 offers a range of new features beside the traditional values of a Shipman Carbon Yacht - short- handed sailing, superb performance, and deckhouse comfort: - Solar power: sun generated electricity - Forward deck lounge area, a private spot in the first row - Protected steering station at the companionway: steering controls, chartplotter, automatic sail handling controls located in a safe, dry and comfortable position under the spraydodger - Protected cockpit: sailing and lounging are not interfering with each other - An extra-large and truly panoramic salon with a 360 degree view\"",
  "descriptionHtml": "<p><strong>Shipman 59 for sale 2014</strong><br> <strong>Shipman 59 for sale </strong>&nbsp;is in very good condition and available for immediate viewings in Valencia, Spain. The carbon yacht Shipman 59 is the ultimate performance blue water cruiser thanks to her short-handed sailing and forward deck lounge area, her integrated Bimini and spray dodger, her protected steering station, the 360º view pilothouse and her carbon-epoxy construction.<br> ''The <strong>Shipman 59 for sale 2014</strong>&nbsp;offers a range of new features beside the traditional values of a Shipman Carbon Yacht - short- handed sailing, superb performance, and deckhouse comfort:<br> - Solar power: sun generated electricity<br> - Forward deck lounge area, a private spot in the first row<br> - Protected steering station at the companionway: steering controls, chartplotter, automatic sail handling controls located in a safe, dry and comfortable position under the spraydodger<br> - Protected cockpit: sailing and lounging are not interfering with each other<br> - An extra-large and truly panoramic salon with a 360 degree view\"</p>",
